## Common Gotchas

- Cart merge direction: always merge INTO database cart, not vice versa
- Concurrent edits: use optimistic locking or last-write-wins
- Inventory re-validation: must check at checkout, not just add-to-cart
- Price changes: decide whether to update prices on page load

## Test Flows

1. Add single item → verify cart state
2. Add same item twice → verify quantity increment
3. Update quantity → verify total recalculation
4. Remove item → verify cart empty state
5. Guest → login → verify cart merge
6. Add item with insufficient inventory → verify error
